OL,3,CMan charged with murdering baby son
OL,5,FA man has been charged with murdering
OL,6,Fhis baby six years after the infant's
OL,7,Fdeath in Leeds.
OL,9,FNiall Worsfold, 29, of Farrow Road,
OL,10,FLeeds, is accused of killing the one-
OL,11,Fmonth-old boy, who died in hospital on
OL,12,F10 July 2020.
OL,14,FThe baby had been admitted to hospital
OL,15,Ffollowing an incident six days earlier
OL,16,Fat an address in Lincombe Drive,
OL,17,FGledhow.
OL,19,FWorsfold has also been charged with
OL,20,Fone count of child cruelty.
